            "title": "蓮塘口岸︱2旅客返深圳驚青過關被截  肚腩大髀走私60部手機︱有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/ca24ea6948ff8e3a060f9d8220807826/2025-03/111_1.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/7006fef4fb6271efb1a45014c1ca0102/f3d884b618f942689e4376396b3ace01-c147b2bc17661771585bd302627824ed-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67cb07e4c867c\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67cb07e4c867f\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"涉事旅客被發現腰間及大腿纏有手機。微博@海關發布\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ee06aa23aa2d5cc080c9fb34c190f848/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250307/_2025030722472521627.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">涉事旅客被發現腰間及大腿纏有手機。微博@海關發布</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>即使明知走私手機隨時被截，仍有人以身犯險偷運大量手機入內地。\n\n</p>\n<p>內地海關總署官方微博發帖，近日，蓮塘海關在旅檢進境渠道查獲人身綁藏走私舊手機60部。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3434728/\">羅湖口岸｜男遊客返內地肛門藏毒 神色匆匆斷正｜有片</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉事旅客經蓮塘口岸入境深圳時被截。微博@海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/555f8979f437798c6a0b1ef4f259e165/2025-03/QFBKjhQOlx08mupj67qE01041200e9v30E010_mp4_snapshot_00_03__2025_03_07_22_26_05_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事旅客經蓮塘口岸入境深圳時被截。微博@海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉事旅客經蓮塘口岸入境深圳時被截。微博@海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d3a563b34c931ef4bc2d283b4f5b5cf1/2025-03/QFBKjhQOlx08mupj67qE01041200e9v30E010_mp4_snapshot_00_04__2025_03_07_22_26_13_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事旅客經蓮塘口岸入境深圳時被截。微博@海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉案人手身纏著多部手機。微博@海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c2d28b747732c535abdc5b2fe99c6342/2025-03/QFBKjhQOlx08mupj67qE01041200e9v30E010_mp4_snapshot_00_07__2025_03_07_22_26_28_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案人手身纏著多部手機。微博@海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉案人手身纏著多部手機。微博@海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/480a83fb994d7d458ea48e483d309422/2025-03/QFBKjhQOlx08mupj67qE01041200e9v30E010_mp4_snapshot_00_12__2025_03_07_22_26_39_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案人手身纏著多部手機。微博@海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉案人手身纏著多部手機。微博@海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/93e93db89fd9bb4efc5eea96fc502a75/2025-03/QFBKjhQOlx08mupj67qE01041200e9v30E010_mp4_snapshot_00_18__2025_03_07_22_26_51_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案人手身纏著多部手機。微博@海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>當日，蓮塘海關關員在進境旅檢大廳進行監管時，發現2名旅客神色緊張、舉止異常，隨即對其進行攔截檢查。<br/>\n<br/>\n<strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3433230/%E8%85%B0%E8%85%BF%E7%B6%81%E8%97%8F%E8%88%8A%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%89%8B%E9%8C%B6-%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%9C%96%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E5%9B%A0%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90%E8%87%83%E8%85%AB%E6%96%B7%E6%AD%A3\" target=\"_blank\">腰腿綁藏舊智能手機手錶 旅客圖澳門入境因「身材臃腫」斷正</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>經進一步檢查，在一名旅客腰部、大腿處查獲用塑料薄膜包裹的舊手機30部，在另一名旅客腰部、腹部處查獲用塑料薄膜包裹的舊手機30部。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2056934/即時-中國-蓮塘口岸︱2旅客返深圳驚青過關被截-肚腩大髀走私60部手機︱有片",
