umbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"葉童fans咩年紀都有。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/417802aba08fd0bb3443eaa8cdacf4db/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_05_01.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉童fans咩年紀都有。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125092/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"攞齊「架生」應援！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef249027679e102c0b2aa8318edcbe39/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_05_04.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        攞齊「架生」應援！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125093/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fans祝葉童青春常駐。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a740ea583b1517169b7508325165f895/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_05_07.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fans祝葉童青春常駐。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125097/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳果揸機與眾人合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3133a809c3033799971d893f8ff03b4/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_06_19.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳果揸機與眾人合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125099/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"葉童狀態大勇，生日願望繼續有得做。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e53c0ddb8b2140178510a6ac6ef5e14/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_06_27.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉童狀態大勇，生日願望繼續有得做。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125085/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"莊思明、楊明出席首映支持《淺淺歲月》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bfaed580d513b1c4524e46c1efcab20d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_07_46.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        莊思明、楊明出席首映支持《淺淺歲月》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125086/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"莊思明 楊明 陳曼娜 杜燕歌 黎燕珊 韓馬利\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f511b1c958d259fcaa65be21c35116a2/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_07_53_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        莊思明 楊明 陳曼娜 杜燕歌 黎燕珊 韓馬利\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125087/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"謝君豪今年想慢活。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/63d8bb6d6ebc2a1cd71d5e156a61b169/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_07_54_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        謝君豪今年想慢活。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125088/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"謝淑芬（白衫）是《淺淺歲月》投資人，賣樓用500萬拍戲悼丈夫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/caec2c1b2ab1c8bef3c61292c5aa661a/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-07_at_20_07_54.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        謝淑芬（白衫）是《淺淺歲月》投資人，賣樓用500萬拍戲悼丈夫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>葉童少出席粉絲聚會</h2>\n<p>講到現場有很多葉童的粉絲，她感謝粉絲的熱情支持，指他們來自不同地方，有些更已看了幾次新戲，她也沒想到會在首映禮上看到這麼多熱情的粉絲，問到她可有粉絲俱樂部？她說：「沒有，我知道他們有自發聚會，我比較少參與聚會，因為我有少少內向，我很感謝他們咁錫我，我唯一可以做的就是做好自己的作品，就是對影迷的回饋。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
