            "title": "世界格蘭披治桌球大獎賽｜新香港人卓林普8強5:0輕取賀辛打入準決賽",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"新香港人卓林普8強5:0輕取賀辛打入準決賽。本報圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/13d6e78b00706d970b5d6a7d2ac879c8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250307/_2025030722352841584.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">新香港人卓林普8強5:0輕取賀辛打入準決賽。本報圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>新香港人卓林普（Judd Trump）在周五的世界格蘭披治桌球大獎賽8強，面對伊朗的賀辛(Hossein Vafaei)戰情一面倒，卓林普第一局即打出一Cue145度，以145:0先拔頭籌。卓林普之後再贏61:0，108:31，116:0，146:0連取5局，在9局5勝制下以局數5:0淘汰賀辛，昂然晉級準決賽。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"伊朗的賀辛8強不敵卓林普。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4757115c3d5bb4c40495baf0fb480903/2025-03/XxjpbeE007474_20250306_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        伊朗的賀辛8強不敵卓林普。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"伊朗的賀辛8強不敵卓林普。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/94447edf221d0e1a0aedcc153db95aae/2025-03/XxjpbeE007476_20250306_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        伊朗的賀辛8強不敵卓林普。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n<