        {
            "title": "博愛歡樂傳萬家丨涂毓麟捐歌酬做善事以表心意  冼靖峰與粉絲做義工處理廚餘  望可舉行個人演唱會",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\" 冼靖峰、涂毓麟今日（7日）為《博愛歡樂傳萬家》綵排。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e6e271cb31ced988c3421a8cde9e2f0e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250307/_2025030721040883061.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"> 冼靖峰、涂毓麟今日（7日）為《博愛歡樂傳萬家》綵排。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>冼靖峰、涂毓麟今日（7日）為《博愛歡樂傳萬家》綵排，兩人表示明晚將會與張馳豪合唱，也會與受惠機構一起唱《獅子山下》，他們指在歌手來說，能與受惠機構一起唱算是福氣。\n\n</p><h2>涂毓麟沒計過捐出多少</h2>\n<p>涂毓麟指每次演出也會捐出歌酬，覺得這是一種心意，但從沒計過捐出多少錢，而冼靖峰也認為這是心意，覺得應是施恩莫望報，又謂平常也有跟粉絲一起做善事，早前就一起去做義工處理廚餘。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"冼靖峰覺得做善事應是施恩莫望報。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0fe3de8f285d8b67ead334375901e9c/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0173.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        冼靖峰覺得做善事應是施恩莫望報。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"冼靖峰表示已有計劃出新歌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/07002e1cb8141c072ca3a8528657a55c/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0174.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        冼靖峰表示已有計劃出新歌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"兩人表示明晚將會與張馳豪合唱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6038c7d708670cb269ec7dfbdd50e28/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0175.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩人表示明晚將會與張馳豪合唱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"冼靖峰今年希望能出多些自己喜愛風格的歌曲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a5e9cda3a19e15e1fca5ff300314fe7/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0176.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        冼靖峰今年希望能出多些自己喜愛風格的歌曲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"二人也會與受惠機構一起唱《獅子山下》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da449403aa2a9b74f1ee85db839fd63b/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0177.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二人也會與受惠機構一起唱《獅子山下》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他們指在歌手來說，能與受惠機構一起唱算是福氣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6b632c05a4ff21b7653089d76575d1e/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0178.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他們指在歌手來說，能與受惠機構一起唱算是福氣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" 涂毓麟指每次演出也會捐出歌酬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/720a4c1d5d80ad4122128a309cb3493a/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0179.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         涂毓麟指每次演出也會捐出歌酬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他覺得這是一種心意，但從沒計過捐出多少錢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5acc11ce27f5e9e2b4d2a2229c05756f/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0180.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他覺得這是一種心意，但從沒計過捐出多少錢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"開騷方面，冼靖峰坦言籌備中，但暫時未能公布。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9f0a0267b6ac80167b77c5b1e819f20c/2025-03/IMG-20250307-WA0182.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        開騷方面，冼靖峰坦言籌備中，但暫時未能公布。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>冼靖峰有計劃出新歌</h2>\n<p>至於工作方面，冼靖峰表示已有計劃出新歌，今年希望能出多些自己喜愛風格的歌曲，至於開騷方面，他坦言籌備中，但暫時未能公布，又謂《聲夢》中有很多人也試過單獨開騷，但自己未試過，故很期待。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
